# P3-3 R4 — chp_gitlab_pr_view /approvals sub-resource fixture.
#
# gitlab_version=17.x
# reference_endpoint=GET /projects/:id/merge_requests/:iid/approvals
# reference_docs=https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/merge_request_approvals.html
#
# Coverage:
#   - `.approved` == true, `.approved_by[]` has 2 approvers (reviewer-a,
#     reviewer-b) so the reviews-synthesis loop projects 2 elements with
#     state:"APPROVED".
#   - top-level `.approved_at` = "2026-01-03T09:00:00Z" — the v17.x recorded
#     probe pinned in R4/§5.1.1 as the source of `reviews[].submittedAt`
#     (GitLab has no per-approver timestamp on this endpoint today).
